## CRM as the spine

Guest CRM (Guest 360) deserves separate emphasis because it's the connective tissue under half the roadmap.

| Feature | Needs Guest CRM |
|---|---|
| Repeat guest / loyalty engine | Yes |
| Email marketing | Yes (segments built on CRM) |
| Review management | Yes (reviews tie back to guests) |
| Social media testimonials | Yes |
| Unified Inbox threads | Yes (messages attach to guests) |
| Attribution / analytics | Yes (LTV per source) |

Without it, each of those features rebuilds its own partial guest view and they don't reconcile. With it, every feature gets richer for free.

### Guest 360 view

```
