## Partner strategy

### Reviews — partner without margin

**Repuso** (Spain/EU strong) and **Revyoos** (broader hotel-focused) both aggregate from 100+ OTAs with schema.org markup for SEO rich snippets. Adapter pattern: `reviews-adapter` interface with multiple implementations, mirroring the CM adapter pattern.

Current state: Repuso account creation via their API, widget embed code manual paste (works in production today). Push partner for API improvement; the workaround is fine until then. Reviews are optional add-on, not critical path — doesn't break 5-minute demo.

### Channel managers — partner without margin

Channex is foundational. Certified Airbnb Connectivity Partner. Provides the official API access GAS could never get directly. Without margin (their pricing is at-cost partnership) but GAS captures the value via everything built on top.

Direct CM integrations (Beds24, Hostaway, Hostfully) — direct APIs. Calry-routed for Smoobu/Lodgify.

### Domains — partner with margin

**OpenSRS (Tucows)** or **Namecheap Reseller** for wholesale domain registration. ~$3-7/year margin per .com, recurring forever on renewals. Avoid GoDaddy (poor reseller margins) and Cloudflare Registrar (at-cost, no margin).

123-Reg (Newfold Digital) — not the right partner for embedding. Fine for personal/internal use.

### Email — partner with margin

**Google Workspace Reseller** or **Microsoft 365 CSP** for mailboxes. ~$5-6/user/mo wholesale, $10-15 retail. Plus forwarding-only option via the domain registrar for cheap-tier customers.

Three-tier email product:
1. **Forwarding** — free or £5-10/yr, MX record on the domain
2. **Real mailbox** — Workspace or 365 under the hood, £10-15/mo retail
3. **Integrated Inbox** — emails threaded into GAS Unified Inbox alongside WhatsApp/FB/booking threads

Tier 3 is the differentiator nobody else has.

### Payments — partner with margin (Stripe Connect)

Already built (OAuth Standard). Migration to Express unlocks `application_fee_amount` on every charge — automatic platform fee. ~0.5-1% per booking is industry-standard for SaaS that hosts payments.

